Description of adult female. Total body length of holotype 0.82 mm . Body (
Fig. 2
) elongate, heavily chitinised and perforated, 8.2 times as long as wide, and thoracomeres and pleomeres telescoping into each other to varying degrees. In lateral view, pleomeres wider than thoracomeres. Head 1.2 times as long as wide, 1.6 times as long as first 2 thoracomeres combined.
